import React from "react";
import {
  Container,
  Row,
  Col,
  Card,
  Image,
  Form,
  Button,
} from "react-bootstrap";
import Logo from "./assets/img/logo-with-out-bg.png";

export default function App() {
  return (
    <Container fluid>
      <Row style={{ height: "100px" }}></Row>
      <Row>
        <Col></Col>
        <Col>
          <Card>
            <Card.Body className="text-center">
              <Image src={Logo} style={{ width: "100px" }} rounded />
              <Card.Title className="text-center">Namaz Tracker</Card.Title>
            </Card.Body>

            <Card.Body>
              <Form>
                <Form.Group>
                  <Button
                    variant="primary"
                    style={{ width: "100%", 
                    backgroundColor: '#25a700'}}
                  >
                    Register
                  </Button> 
                </Form.Group>
                <Button
                  variant="primary"
                  style={{ width: "100%" , backgroundColor: '#6f6f6f' }}
                >
                  Login
                </Button>
              </Form>
            </Card.Body>
          </Card>
        </Col>
        <Col></Col>
      </Row>
    </Container>
  );
}
